headline: With Layoffs Spreading Across Industries, These Careers Are Still 'Doing Fine Right Now'—And Some Are Surprisingly Easy To Get Into
summary: Despite the wave of layoffs and hiring freezes hitting major sectors like tech, not every career path is suffering. A Reddit thread asking people what fields are “doing fine right now” received hundreds of replies; many of them from people currently working and thriving in those industries.
